Package: bundlephobia.com
Title: npm Bundle Size (Bundlephobia) API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Bundlephobia API. Get minified and gzipped bundle sizes for npm packages. Includes LLM context injection via bundlephobia_context().
